casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Stacy Lee BROWN, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157856
COA: 342457 Supreme Court of Michigan. October 30, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the April 10, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
